title: MisterMusic Show 314 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 314 [2 hours] 192kbps MP3 Stereo.

On this week's MisterMusic Show new tunes from Weezer, The Raveonettes,
Wolfgang, and Francisco The Man.
Plus a huge hit song is the 'Oldie of the Week' from July 1986. It was number one in the US and Canada that summer-and holds the title of 'most played music video on Mtv'.
And the usual mix of indie, alternative and classic hits from the past to keep you groovin' for two hours.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
